item.title: How do i change the speed of leveling
item.dc:creator: @bmxr4c3r709 bmxr4c3r709
item.description:
@bmxr4c3r709 wrote:

Okay, right click on whatever you want to change the speed of, A door for example It would say ‘Examine Door(1531)’. So go into your client.java, search for case 1531
and change the actionTimer(Not the first one, the second one) to say… 20, or in your case probably 27 or 28 would work.
